for s in range(1,34):
    r1 = 1
    r2 = 1
    r3 = 1
    density = s
    theta_d = 2*np.pi/density
    n_d = density
    x = np.zeros(density)
    y = np.zeros(density)
    for i in range(0,density):
        x[i] = np.cos(theta_d*i)
        y[i] = np.sin(theta_d*i)

    circum = s
    xs = x
    ys = y
    for p in range(0,circum):
        xi = np.zeros(density)
        yi = np.zeros(density)
        for i in range(0,density):
            xi[i] = x[p]+i*np.cos(theta_d*i)
            yi[i] = y[p]+i*np.sin(theta_d*i)
        xs = np.append(xs,xi)
        ys = np.append(ys,yi)
    
    tit = ''
    ss = str(s)
    if (s % 2 == 0):
        tit = tit.join(['Even, s =',ss])
    else:
        tit = tit.join(['Odd, s =',ss])
        
    plt.scatter(xs,ys)
    plt.axis('equal')
    plt.title(tit)
    plt.show()

for s in range(3,34):
    r1 = 1
    r2 = 4
    r3 = 1
    density = s
    theta_d = 2*np.pi/density
    n_d = density
    x = np.zeros(density)

        x[i] = np.cos(theta_d*i)
        y[i] = np.sin(theta_d*i)

    circum = s
    xs = x
    ys = y
    for p in range(0,circum):

for s in np.linspace(5,105,5):
    r1 = 1
    r2 = 4
    r3 = 10
    density = int(s)
    theta_d = 2*np.pi/density
    n_d = density
    x = np.zeros(density)
    y = np.zeros(density)
    for i in range(0,density):
        x[i] = np.cos(theta_d*i)
        y[i] = np.sin(theta_d*i)

    circum = int(s)
    xs = x
    ys = y
    for p in range(0,circum):
        xi = np.zeros(density)
        yi = np.zeros(density)
        for i in range(0,density):
            xi[i] = (r3+i)*x[p]+r2*np.cos(theta_d*i)
            yi[i] = (r3+p)*y[p]+r2*np.sin(theta_d*i)
        xs = np.append(xs,xi)
        ys = np.append(ys,yi)
    
    tit = ''
    ss = str(s)
    if (s % 2 == 0):
        tit = tit.join(['Even, s =',ss])
    else:
        tit = tit.join(['Odd, s =',ss])
        
    plt.scatter(xs,ys)
    plt.axis('equal')
    plt.title(tit)
    plt.show()
